<subSubSection box="[198,1392,346,372]" pageId="13" pageNumber="54" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="13.[151,1436,266,572]" box="[198,1392,346,372]" pageId="13" pageNumber="54">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,326,346,372]" pageId="13" pageNumber="54">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
None to one weak preopercular spine; dorsal fin with 2 distinct ocelli and none in anal fin.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[198,1220,386,412]" pageId="13" pageNumber="54" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="13.[151,1436,266,572]" box="[198,1220,386,412]" pageId="13" pageNumber="54">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,359,386,412]" pageId="13" pageNumber="54">Distribution.</emphasis>
